BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:XnSyTLU_6r-fH2mfEAcou
SUMMARY:Michael McIntyre: Hello America!
DTSTAMP:20260317T041448Z
DTSTART:20260327T030000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Paramount Theatre is located in downtown Seattle at 911 Pin
	e Street\, Seattle\, WA 98101. There is an overall 8 ticket limit per patr
	on. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will have their orders canceled at 
	the venue's discretion. All sales are final. No refunds or exchanges. Mobi
	le barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue reserves the right 
	to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have
	 a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no elevator. Stai
	rs only to the balcony level.\n12+ recommended age limit. TM+ Resale has b
	een disabled. Metal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive early. No weapo
	ns. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing ADA accessible seatin
	g\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance is needed with a
	ccommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at accessibility@stg
	presents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless freestanding chair fo
	r patrons with mobility impairments and their companions. Please note that
